OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FThames Water has revealed a proposal
OL,7,Fto secure up to #3 billion in new cash
OL,8,Ffrom creditors as it seeks to bolster
OL,9,Fits finances and avoid the threat of
OL,10,Fnationalisation.
OL,12,FThe struggling utilities giant has put
OL,13,Fforward the deal amid continued
OL,14,Fefforts to restructure its significant
OL,15,Fdebt pile.
