OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FChris Weston, chief executive of the
OL,7,Fwater supplier, said the transaction
OL,8,Fwould deliver "further progress to put
OL,9,FThames Water on to a more stable
OL,10,Ffinancial footing as we seek a long-
OL,11,Fterm solution" to its financial
OL,12,Ftroubles.
OL,14,FIt said it only has #500 million in
OL,15,Fcash to support the company, as well
OL,16,Fas another #500 million for its
OL,17,Freserves and compensation payments.
