OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FThames Water, which serves about 16
OL,7,Fmillion people, is in the grip of a
OL,8,Ffunding crisis and previously said it
OL,9,Fonly has enough cash to continue
OL,10,Foperating until May 2025.
OL,12,FIt also has more than #15 billion of
OL,13,Fdebt, and regulator Ofwat has said it
OL,14,Fintends to appoint an independent
OL,15,Fmonitor to supervise the company as it
OL,16,Fattempts a turnaround.
OL,18,FThe water company said its debt is due
OL,19,Fto swell to #17.9 billion by March
OL,20,Fnext year.
