OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FHowever, on Friday it said it has
OL,7,Fbrokered a deal with some of its
OL,8,Fcreditors for the transaction to
OL,9,F"extend its liquidity runway".
OL,11,FIt said the deal would involve an
OL,12,Finitial #1.5 billion, supported by a
OL,13,Fnumber of its creditors.
OL,15,FThis funding will tide the company
OL,16,Fover until October next year, the
OL,17,Fcompany said.
