OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FThere would be capacity for a further
OL,7,F#1.5 billion, across two tranches of
OL,8,F#750 million, if Thames Water makes an
OL,9,Fappeal to the Competition and Markets
OL,10,FAuthority (CMA) regulator over its
OL,11,Ffinal determination for the water
OL,12,Fsector.
OL,14,FThe CMA is expected to confirm in
OL,15,FDecember how much it will allow water
OL,16,Fcompanies to increase their bills by
OL,17,Fover the next five years.
