OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FWater firms have requested increases
OL,7,Fwhich would see the average consumer
OL,8,Fbill in England and Wales rise by 40%
OL,9,Fbetween now and 2030, costing #615 per
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThames Water has called for its
OL,13,Fcustomers to face a 53% increase.
OL,15,FSecuring the second cash boost of #1.5
OL,16,Fbillion would fund the company until
OL,17,FMay 2026.
