OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FThames Water said the fresh funding
OL,7,Fdeal will need court approval, with an
OL,8,Finitial hearing due on December 17.
OL,9,FThe process is expected to complete by
OL,10,Flate January.
OL,12,FSir Adrian Montague, chairman of
OL,13,FThames Water, said: "The board and
OL,14,Fleadership team remain focused on
OL,15,Fstabilising the business, and today's
OL,16,Fannouncement is an important step in
OL,17,Fthe process to increase its long-term
OL,18,Ffinancial resilience.
