OL,3,CThames Water launches plan to raise up
OL,4,Cto #3bn in emergency funding
OL,6,FMr Weston added: "We are working
OL,7,Fclosely with and have the support of
OL,8,Four creditors, enabling Thames to
OL,9,Fcontinue to implement our turnaround
OL,10,Fplan so that we can deliver better
OL,11,Fresults for our customers and the
OL,12,Fenvironment whilst seeking to attract
OL,13,Fnew capital into the business.
OL,15,F"In the meantime, our teams on the
OL,16,Fground continue to supply our services
OL,17,Fto our 16 million customers every day."
